## Project 2: Log Anomaly Detection

### Objective
Identify abnormal patterns in login activity using time-based analysis.

### Key Findings
- Observed distribution of login events across time intervals
- Identified spikes in failed login attempts
- Detected abnormal activity patterns indicating potential attack behavior

### Conclusion
Time-based aggregation revealed anomalies in failed login frequency, demonstrating how attackers generate detectable spikes in log data.
